<item>
            <title>[LU-16759] MOFED 5.5 and later is broken on [open]SUSE 15 sp3</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16759</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;MOFED 5.5 fails with:&lt;br/&gt;
ERROR: &quot;ib_dma_virt_map_sg&quot; &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;.../ko2iblnd.ko&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; undefined!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This occurs due to:&lt;br/&gt;
ib_dma_map_sg() -&amp;gt; ib_dma_virt_map_sg() which is defined but not exported by NVidia&apos;s MOFED drivers.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
